---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Cookie Policy - Boxing Timer Champ">
	<main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-8">
		<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Cookie Policy</h1>
		<p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">Last updated: April 4, 2025</p>

		<section class="mb-8">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">1. What are Cookies?</h2>
			<p class="mb-4">Cookies are small text files that are stored on your device when you visit our website. They help us provide you with a better experience by remembering your preferences and improving our services.</p>
		</section>

		<section class="mb-8">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">2. Types of Cookies We Use</h2>
			<h3 class="text-xl font-medium mb-3">A. Strictly Necessary Cookies</h3>
			<ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
				<li>These cookies are essential for our website to function properly.</li>
				<li>They enable basic functions like page navigation and access to secure areas.</li>
				<li>These cookies cannot be disabled.</li>
			</ul>

			<h3 class="text-xl font-medium mb-3">B. Analytics Cookies</h3>
			<ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
				<li>These cookies help us understand how visitors interact with our website.</li>
				<li>They provide us with anonymous information about page views, click-through rates, and other metrics.</li>
				<li>You can choose to disable these cookies through our cookie consent banner.</li>
			</ul>
		</section>

		<section class="mb-8">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">3. Third-Party Cookies</h2>
			<p class="mb-4">To support and improve our services, we use cookies from trusted third-party providers. These tools help us understand how visitors interact with the site, manage tags efficiently, and deliver a better overall experience. Services currently in use include:</p>
			<ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
				<li>Google Analytics – for collecting anonymous usage statistics</li>
				<li>Google Tag Manager – for managing analytics and tracking tags</li>
				<li>Hotjar – for gaining insight into user interactions through anonymized heatmaps and session recordings</li>
				<li>Embedded content platforms – such as YouTube, for video playback</li>
				<li>Social media integrations – such as sharing buttons or embedded posts from third-party platforms</li>
			</ul>
			<p class="mb-4">You can control these cookies through your browser settings or the third-party's cookie consent manager.</p>
		</section>

		<section class="mb-8">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">4. Your Cookie Preferences</h2>
			<p class="mb-4">You can manage your cookie preferences in several ways:</p>
			<ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
				<li>Through our cookie consent banner</li>
				<li>By adjusting your browser settings</li>
				<li>By clearing your browser cache and cookies</li>
			</ul>
			<p class="mb-4">Please note that disabling certain cookies may affect your experience on our website.</p>
		</section>

		<section class="mb-8">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">5. How to Control Cookies</h2>
			<p class="mb-4">Most web browsers allow you to:</p>
			<ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
				<li>Block all cookies</li>
				<li>Allow only certain types of cookies</li>
				<li>Delete stored cookies</li>
				<li>Notify you when a website is trying to place a cookie</li>
			</ul>
			<p class="mb-4">For more information about controlling cookies in your browser, please refer to your browser's help documentation.</p>
		</section>

		<section class="mb-8">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">6. Changes to This Policy</h2>
			<p class="mb-4">We may update our Cookie Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page and the date of the last update will be revised. We encourage you to review this policy periodically for any changes.</p>
		</section>

		<section class="mb-8">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">7. Contact Us</h2>
			<p class="mb-4">If you have any questions about our Cookie Policy, please contact us at:</p>
			<p class="mb-4">Email: support@boxingtimerchamp.com</p>
			<p class="mb-4">You can also use our <a href="/contact" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">Contact Form</a> to reach out to us.</p>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>
